  {
    "client_msg_id": "e917b8bb-3219-456e-83c6-b5ca3e5adfca",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "One of the solutions to this bias is to work closely with novices, which can help us develop an understanding of which concepts are difficult and why through observing the novice grapple with concepts.",
